Rick,

I&#39;m not sure, but I would be wary of trying to equilibrate mixtures  
that are not charge neutral. I&#39;d have to look at the code, but I  
think there may be something that enforces charge neutrality.  You  
might try balancing the electron concentration with Ar+, to make a  
charge-neutral mixture.

Dave


